steps.step: {"blocks":[{"key":"dj1k","text":"For HEK293t cells, plate 50,000 cells/well in 0.5 mL of DMEM on 24-well plate the day prior.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"8itpq","text":"30+ min before spinfection, make sure the table-top centrifuge is at 30 °C .","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"dsjec","text":"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"3l88v","text":"Virus amount","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"d6aup","text":"Virus titer will vary, so it is useful to add different amounts of virus to well to determine the appropriate titer. For a well of a 24-well plate, virus amounts can range from 5 μL to 500 μL.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"4hqdt","text":"Polybrene amount","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"77fp3","text":"For most cell types polybrene increases infection efficiency and should be used at a final concentration of 8 μg/mL. Example dilution: add 0.8 uL (160 μg) polybrene stock (stock at 100mg/mL) to 0.5 mL media.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"4vnl0","text":"Spin at 1000 rcf for 2 hrs at 30 C. ","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"e6hbh","text":"  ","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[{"key":0,"offset":0,"length":1}],"data":{}},{"key":"e9upn","text":"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{"0":{"type":"centrifuge","mutability":"MUTABLE","data":{"centrifuge":"1000","duration":0,"error_centrifuge":false,"error_temperature":false,"guid":"F2E63460648E11EDBF3E4F247D52E3E0","id":0,"label":"","pause":null,"preset":[],"scientificNotation":{"centrifuge":false,"temperature":false},"start":null,"temperature":"30","temperatureUnit":10,"unit":1324}}}}
{"blocks":[{"key":"akrt","text":"It is OK if the temperature starts off between 20-30C.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"63r3l","text":"Remove plate from centrifuge and place in hood. Douse with ethanol and wait 10 minutes. Place in incubator.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}
